"A.P.238/4/8": "Yo, partner. How's your mission going? I've made no progress on mine."
"I guess aimlessly searching around like this is starting to get to me, but I don't really mind."
"Say, aren't they holding that Battle Championship thing soon? Eh? You're taking part, too?"
"It's not that I want to do something like that, but... Well, a change of pace might be just the thing."
"The way things are now, I've done about all I can... Hmm... If you're going for it, I might do too."
"Breakthroughs can come from the last place you'd expect... Alright, yeah, let's do it."
"I mean, if you're OK with that, partner?"
"Only, there's a rule that you have to work with someone else."
"Heheh, later! Send me an invite on the day!"
